<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Abraham's Blog</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/</link><description/><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 25 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.inshomepgup.com/post/git/skills/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>README</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/readme/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/readme/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="实用git技能合集">实用Git技能合集
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>最近很长一段时间大概是GUI用的太多了，导致基本的CLI操作已经逐渐回归最简单的Hello world了(git add . git commit git push)&lt;/p></description><category>git</category></item><item><title>使用B分支的单个文件覆盖A分支的单个文件</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8b%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96a%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8b%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96a%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git switch A
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git checkout B [file_name]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git checkout [目标分支] [目标文件]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description><category>git</category></item><item><title>还原单个文件到指定的版本</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/%E8%BF%98%E5%8E%9F%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%B0%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/%E8%BF%98%E5%8E%9F%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%B0%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git reset &amp;lt;commit_id&amp;gt; &amp;lt;file_path&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git reset ec6effa43a9e4b800f16c209d5229b24e1e43841 src/views/custom/components/Form/ItemComponents/ItemOptionList.vue
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description><category>git</category></item><item><title>删除分支，强制删除</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="删除">删除
&lt;/h3>&lt;h5 id="如果去删除一个未合并的分支会有提示">如果去删除一个未合并的分支会有提示。
&lt;/h5>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git br -d feat/A
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">error: the branch &amp;#39;feat/A&amp;#39; is not fully merged
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hint: If you are sure you want to delete it, run &amp;#39;git branch -D feat/A&amp;#39;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hint: Disable this message with &amp;#34;git config advice.forceDeleteBranch false&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="执行强制删除">执行强制删除
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git br -D feat/A
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Deleted branch feat/A (was 83ec5ad).
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description><category>git</category></item><item><title>分支</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/p/%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF/</guid><description>&lt;p>拉取远程分支并创建本地分支来追踪远程分支&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"># 先拉取远程的更新到本地
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git fetch origin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"># 创建本地分支并且自动追踪
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git switch -t origin/develop
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>git switch -t 远程仓库/远程分支&lt;/p>
&lt;p>-t:&amp;ndash;track 设置追踪&lt;/p></description><category>git</category></item></channel></rss>